---
---

<section
  id="inicio"
  data-track-section="home_hero"
  class="relative isolate overflow-hidden border-b border-white/10 bg-brand-black"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_top_left,rgba(212,175,55,0.16),transparent_38%),radial-gradient(circle_at_85%_18%,rgba(139,92,246,0.12),transparent_34%),linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.04),transparent)]"></div>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30 [background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,0.07)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,0.07)_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:34px_34px]"></div>

  <div class="relative mx-auto flex min-h-[calc(100svh-5rem)] max-w-7xl flex-col justify-between px-6 pb-14 pt-28 md:pb-20 md:pt-32">
    <div class="max-w-4xl">
      <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 rounded-full border border-brand-gold/30 bg-brand-gold/10 px-4 py-2 text-[11px] font-black uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-brand-gold">
        JS Solutions
        <span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-brand-gold"></span>
        IA aplicada a operaciones reales
      </p>

      <h1 class="mt-8 max-w-5xl text-balance text-5xl font-bold leading-[0.95] text-white md:text-7xl lg:text-[5.4rem]">
        Tu operacion puede crecer
        <span class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gold-gradient">
          sin perder claridad.
        </span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-brand-off-white/78 md:text-xl">
        Esta entrada principal te ayuda a elegir el camino correcto segun tu
        realidad: crecimiento comercial para empresas o atencion ciudadana para
        entidades. Sin ruido tecnico en el primer vistazo.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 grid gap-4 md:mt-16 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr] md:items-end">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
        <a
          href="/pymes"
          data-track="sector_selector_click"
          data-track-label="Ir a PyMES"
          data-track-location="home_hero"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-gold-gradient px-7 py-4 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-black transition-transform duration-300 hover:scale-[1.02]"
        >
          Ir a PyMES
        </a>
        <a
          href="/sector-publico"
          data-track="sector_selector_click"
          data-track-label="Ir a Sector Publico"
          data-track-location="home_hero"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-white/15 px-7 py-4 text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-white transition-colors duration-300 hover:border-brand-gold/60 hover:text-brand-gold"
        >
          Ir a Sector Publico
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-lg justify-self-end border-l border-white/10 pl-5 text-sm leading-relaxed text-brand-off-white/64">
        Empieza por la ruta que se parece a tu operacion. Luego bajamos esa
        experiencia a tus reglas, tu equipo y tus canales reales.
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
